                    <h2 data-uuid="a9430cc1e53d4ed28f69dd8f013c203c">Copperheads Political Cartoon</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="8fa638fc93b2493d82628ad045e4d2b7">This political cartoon is making fun of Copperhead northerners who want peace. The cartoon implies that the Copperheads’ plan to get the Confederacy to rejoin the Union is to bore them into it.</p>
